create a force_set file
==========================

input
no. of cases e.g 40
displacement file e.g. disp.yaml
OUTCAR files (for 40 cases 40 OUTCAR files)

process
read data from displacement file
read positions of atoms from outcar file (start from word POSITION and end on total drift)
create a new file contains data from both files in specific order.

output
The name of output file is FORCE_SETS
